&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;THE ROLE:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;We are currently hiring a Personal Assistant to help support our London Leadership team, on a 12-month fixed term contract.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The role requires someone who is organised, proactive and an excellent multitasker. In this role, you’ll be providing invaluable support to leaders within the business, working at pace to meet the demands of our fast paced agency.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a great opportunity for an experienced PA looking to develop their career. You&#39;ll have significant exposure to our Senior Executives, while partnering with colleagues across a variety of disciplines throughout the agency. This breadth of exposure offers the opportunity to build relationships across multiple functions and gain insight into a diverse range of specialisms and ways of working.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
